
___________________

       Keyboard  
   ________________
      
   
   NEWLINE (RETURN)
   
      Cursor is automatically intendated. The amount of intendation is 
      determenied by the position of first non whitespace character on 
      previous line.
      
   BACKSPACE
   
      Nothing special here, I reckon.
      
   TABULATOR
   
      Always inserts a specified number of spaces.
      
   DELETE
   
      Nothing special here, I think.         

   CURSOR UP, CURSOR DOWN, CURSOR LEFT, CURSOR RIGHT
   
      The cursor may be move freely in any direction by using the cursor-keys.
  
